      "description": "Optional structured metadata capturing the SLSA adoption challenges and mitigation strategies relevant to a given attestation or deployment context. Derived from empirical analysis of 1,523 SLSA-related GitHub issues across 233 repositories (Tamanna et al., 2024, arXiv:2409.05014). Use this class to document which challenge themes apply to the current deployment and which strategies are being employed or recommended. Attach via the adoptionMetadata slot on SlsaDocument.",
